document_data.mainbody:
The Bloody Keel was the ship of the fiery red haired rogue Sheila Kree. It received its name from the punishment its captain exacted upon those who did not obey, [http//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Keelhauling keelhauling].
Catti-brie sank the Bloody Keel by shooting the helmsman as Sheila Kree and her band was making a hasty escape from her cove. With no one at the helm, the Bloody Keel crashed against the rocks and sank.
